snippet.title: Hugh Grant & More Stars To Appear In Netflix Comedy Special 'Death To 2021'
snippet.description:
Netflix has announced a new all-star year-end special “Death to 2021”, starring Hugh Grant, Lucy Liu, William Jackson Harper and more. Morgan Hoffman and Carlos Bustamante react on ET Canada Live.

#DeathTo2021 #Netflix #HughGrant
